	termtag = "Security";
	doc_title_1 = "Security Notice";
	doc_content_1 = "The last NRC review noted several security concerns that have been rectified urgently in the interests of national security.<br>1: Due to increased trespass, a new security booth has been installed at road access as a deterrent. We expect this to be manned.<br>2: Administrative employees in the northern offices are gaining unauthorised access to the plant through the utility tunnel. This tunnel is now secured and further abuse of it shall result in termination for the employee(s) involved. <br>3: No more pets are allowed onsite. Animals are not capable of adhering to our strict regulations, and on a more personal note, I don't want what happens when a cat jumps into our reactor ever again.<br>Chief Wickers"
